ness to develop).\n**Recommendation:** Candidate\u202fB is the best overall fit for the long\u2011distance pilot position.\nMETADATA_JSON:\n{\"agent\": \"agent_1\", \"vote\": \"Candidate B\"}", "thoughts": "We need to produce final contribution as agent_1. We have already seen that agent_1 already gave a public message and vote for Candidate B in round 1. Now round 2, we need to respond again. We must consider if we have any new info to ask. The discussion so far: Agent 1 gave assessment and vote B. Agent 2 gave assessment and vote B. Agent 3 gave assessment and vote B. Now as Agent 1 again, we need to contribute. According to guidelines, we should consider if we have any missing info. We have asked about D teamwork, got no info. We have asked about A reliability, B decision speed, C willingness, got answers. So we have all info. We could either reaffirm B or raise concerns. But we must follow the instruction: \"Handle the requests as specified in the System Instruction.\" The system instruction is to choose best candidate. So we need to give our final contribution, maybe reaffirm B. We could also ask if any other agent has info about candidate D leadership strengths? But we already have weak leadership. No new info.\n\nThus we can produce a public message summarizing reasoning and vote B. Ensure we only use given attributes. Provide METADATA_JSON with agent_1 and vote Candidate B.\n\nLet's produce."}
